        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThinking about it, we may have to do the same thing for references to policy-* living in different repositories as we release one by one ..  although I don't have a good handle now with the new release process.   I think the mvn version plugin won't resolve snapshot dependencies across repos and will need to ensure all those don't point to snapshots (outside the repo, even for policy ones).   I think .. not 100% sure.",
